trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" /> class is used with a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> object to move an LDAP object from one domain to another.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" /> é usada com um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ModifyDNRequest" /> para mover um objeto LDAP de um domínio para outro.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The DNS name of the destination domain controller.
trans-unit.target: O nome DNS do controlador de domínio de destino.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.#ctor(System.String)" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" /> class using the specified target domain.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.#ctor(System.String)" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" /> usando o domínio de destino especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.GetValue" /> method returns the binary representation of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" />.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.GetValue" /> retorna a representação binária do <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.TargetDomainController" /> property gets or sets the DNS name of the destination domain controller (DC).
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.CrossDomainMoveControl.TargetDomainController" /> obtém ou define o nome DNS do controlador de domínio de destino.

trans-unit.source: The DNS name of the destination DC.
trans-unit.target: O nome DNS do controlador de domínio de destino.
